{"tid":876187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑到仆街] 華春瑩幽默串爆︰「美方有些人應角逐奧斯卡最佳劇本獎」","createTime":"2018-10-25T12:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T13:35:16.000Z","uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c74e91a3ec743e63c00217ad125fe1a84e2e8d20","tid":876187,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"美與中俄角力升級之際，美國《紐約時報》報道，美國總統特朗普使用iPhone通話時，遭中國和俄羅斯間諜竊聽。在北京，外交部發言人質疑是「假新聞」，又表示如果很擔心蘋果手機被竊聽，可改用中國的華為手機。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩今日在例行記者會上表示，看到了相關報道，「<span style=\"color: red;\">感覺美方有些人真是在不遺餘力地角逐奧斯卡最佳劇本獎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n她又提出三點看法，一是《紐約時報》應該知道，發表類似的報道，「<span style=\"color: red;\">只會多一個在做fake news（假新聞）的證據</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」；<span style=\"color: red;\">二是如果很擔心蘋果手機被竊聽的話，可以改用華為手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；三是為了絕對安全起見，可以停止使用任何現代通訊設備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。據指，華春瑩提及華為時，在場人士哄堂大笑。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2193402/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AEiPhone%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%8A%E8%81%BD%20%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%A5%E7%91%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2193402%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AEiPhone%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%258A%25E8%2581%25BD%2520%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2598%25A5%25E7%2591%25A9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA&d=fgFrnIcvcWuwYkN8wU6h4RFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=269ec819\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2193402/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AEiPhone%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%8A%E8%81%BD%20%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%A5%E7%91%A9%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部開始有幽默感, 句句串爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fdec98043d427fc617853cc747f601e5c9854a","tid":876187,"uid":23400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"習老師而家個樣咪好似個喪家之犬咁，見到都想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c01552285dbc9cb52295c0ce4561bd2427733ef","tid":876187,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外交部開始識玩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一於趁中期選舉黎緊玩到佢仆街"},{"pid":"0aa4d47920efeca3abdebf400908987777b40cc2","tid":876187,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5feebe3364048391e6541bb944f4b2b43db9344","tid":876187,"uid":97882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"同現場觀眾夾定左架。<br />\n<br />\n拿陣間呀姐就會咁咁咁搞下笑，大家記住俾多兩錢肉緊，標眼水加五十，瀨埋屎一百。"},{"pid":"2412a2523246b7d8e1636dafaee3e42c016ff9d8","tid":876187,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"有無片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi